defaultChannel 4 believes that the BBC should seek to partner more with fellow PSBs especially in the case of developing technology and distributing content. The BBC spends many millions of the licence fee on research and development, much of which is focussed o
defaultn their online proposition and on the iPlayer while other PSBs also develop their own broadly similar propositions in isolation from each other. 
defaultWere the BBC to partner with other PSBs and share technology it would doubtless save PSBs 
defaultsignificant amounts
default 
defaultof time and money
